```javascript
db.minutes.createSearchIndex("default", {
  "mappings": {
    "fields": {
      "text": {
        "type": "document",
        "fields": {
          "en_US": {
            "type": "string",
            "analyzer": "tokenTrimmer" 
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "analyzers": [
    {
      "name": "tokenTrimmer",
      "charFilters": [{
        "type": "htmlStrip",
        "ignoredTags": ["a"]
      }],
      "tokenizer": {
        "type": "keyword"
      },
      "tokenFilters": [
        {
          "type": "trim"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
})

```

**Input:**

```json
db.minutes.aggregate([
  {
    "$search": {
      "wildcard": {
        "query": "*department meetings*",
        "path": "text.en_US",
        "allowAnalyzedField": true
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "$project": {
      "_id": 1,
      "text.en_US": 1
    }
  }
])
```

**Output:**

```json
[
  {
    _id: 1,
    text: { en_US: '<head> This page deals with department meetings. </head>' }
  }
]
